0.7.name: wordpress/leaf
0.7.description: The Leaf theme is a stylish and customizable WordPress theme. Make it yours with the easy customizable theme options. Uses Superfish menu effects, built-in pagination for post pages, special styles for eight different post formats, and a responsive layout for mobile devices.
